prompts.frontCover: A charming and humorous cartoon illustration of a giant boba milk tea cup lounging on a beautiful, minimalist beach. The boba cup is personified with cute cartoon eyes and a relaxed smile, wearing sunglasses and holding a tiny beach umbrella. The "tapioca pearls" at the bottom of the cup are replaced with miniature, perfectly round cartoon coconuts. The scene is set against a simple, clean background with stylized, gentle waves lapping the shore and a single, elegant palm tree. The color palette is soft and pastel. Centered in the middle of the design, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao". The overall style is flat 2D vector art, minimalist with clean lines and simple shapes.
